  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this study is to look for the interest forecast of the IPS as
      infra-clinical cardiovascular marker in the prediction of a change of the cognitive functions
      (MCI) at the elderly of 70 and more years old without clinical cardiovascular pathology.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
